# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# EDUGEST DZ — Configuration Environnement
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# 1. Copier ce fichier : cp .env.example .env
# 2. Générer APP_KEY      : php artisan key:generate
# 3. Générer JWT_SECRET    : php artisan jwt:secret
# 4. Configurer DB_HOST, DB_DATABASE, DB_USERNAME, DB_PASSWORD
# 5. Lancer : php artisan migrate --seed
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Application ──────────────────────────────────────────
APP_NAME="EduGest DZ"
APP_ENV=local
APP_KEY=
APP_DEBUG=true
APP_TIMEZONE="Africa/Algiers"
APP_URL=http://localhost
APP_LOCALE=fr
APP_FALLBACK_LOCALE=fr
APP_FAKER_LOCALE=fr_FR
APP_MAINTENANCE_DRIVER=file
APP_MAINTENANCE_STORE=database
APP_PREVIOUS_KEYS=

# ── Base de Données PostgreSQL ──────────────────────────
DB_CONNECTION=pgsql
DB_HOST=postgres
DB_PORT=5432
DB_DATABASE=edugestdz
DB_USERNAME=edugest_user
DB_PASSWORD=
DB_CHARSET=utf8
DB_SCHEMA=public
DB_QUEUE_CONNECTION=
DB_QUEUE_TABLE=jobs
DB_QUEUE_RETRY_AFTER=90

# ── Redis ────────────────────────────────────────────────
REDIS_CLIENT=phpredis
REDIS_HOST=redis
REDIS_PORT=6379
REDIS_PASSWORD=
REDIS_DB=0
REDIS_CACHE_DB=1
REDIS_QUEUE_DB=2
REDIS_SESSION_DB=3
REDIS_PERSISTENT=false

# ── Cache & Sessions ─────────────────────────────────────
CACHE_STORE=redis
CACHE_PREFIX=
SESSION_DRIVER=redis
SESSION_LIFETIME=120
SESSION_ENCRYPT=false

# ── Queue (Redis) ────────────────────────────────────────
QUEUE_CONNECTION=redis
REDIS_QUEUE_CONNECTION=default
QUEUE_FAILED_DRIVER=database-uuids

# ── JWT Auth ─────────────────────────────────────────────
JWT_SECRET=
JWT_TTL=1440
JWT_REFRESH_TTL=20160
JWT_ALGO=HS256
JWT_BLACKLIST_ENABLED=true
JWT_BLACKLIST_GRACE_PERIOD=0
JWT_LEEWAY=0

# ── Email (SMTP / Mailpit en dev) ────────────────────────
MAIL_MAILER=smtp
MAIL_HOST=mailpit
MAIL_PORT=1025
MAIL_USERNAME=null
MAIL_PASSWORD=null
MAIL_ENCRYPTION=null
MAIL_FROM_ADDRESS="noreply@edugestdz.dz"
MAIL_FROM_NAME="${APP_NAME}"

# ── Logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
LOG_CHANNEL=stack
LOG_STACK=single,daily
LOG_LEVEL=debug
LOG_DAILY_DAYS=14
LOG_DEPRECATIONS_CHANNEL=null
LOG_DEPRECATIONS_TRACE=false

# ── Stockage & Cloud ─────────────────────────────────────
FILESYSTEM_DISK=local
AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=
AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=
AWS_DEFAULT_REGION=eu-west-3
AWS_BUCKET=edugestdz
AWS_URL=
AWS_USE_PATH_STYLE_ENDPOINT=false

# ── Meilisearch (Full-Text Search) ───────────────────────
SCOUT_DRIVER=meilisearch
SCOUT_QUEUE=true
MEILISEARCH_HOST=http://meilisearch:7700
MEILISEARCH_KEY=

# ── Satim — Paiement CIB / Dahabia / BaridiMob ──────────
SATIM_TERMINAL_ID=
SATIM_MERCHANT_ID=
SATIM_PASSWORD=
SATIM_URL=https://test.satim.dz/payment/rest
SATIM_SANDBOX=true

# ── SMS — Twilio ─────────────────────────────────────────
TWILIO_SID=
TWILIO_TOKEN=
TWILIO_FROM=

# ── Push Notifications — Firebase ────────────────────────
FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=
FIREBASE_CREDENTIALS=firebase-credentials.json

# ── Messagerie — SendGrid / Mailgun ──────────────────────
SENDGRID_API_KEY=
MAILGUN_DOMAIN=
MAILGUN_SECRET=

# ── WhatsApp Business API ────────────────────────────────
WHATSAPP_API_TOKEN=
WHATSAPP_PHONE_ID=
WHATSAPP_API_URL=https://graph.facebook.com/v18.0
WHATSAPP_VERIFY_TOKEN=edugest_verify

# ── WebSockets — Pusher ──────────────────────────────────
PUSHER_APP_ID=
PUSHER_APP_KEY=
PUSHER_APP_SECRET=
PUSHER_HOST=
PUSHER_PORT=443
PUSHER_SCHEME=https
PUSHER_APP_CLUSTER=mt1
VITE_PUSHER_APP_KEY="${PUSHER_APP_KEY}"
VITE_PUSHER_HOST="${PUSHER_HOST}"
VITE_PUSHER_PORT="${PUSHER_PORT}"
VITE_PUSHER_SCHEME="${PUSHER_SCHEME}"
VITE_PUSHER_APP_CLUSTER="${PUSHER_APP_CLUSTER}"

# ── CORS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:5173,http://localhost:3000

# ── Multi-Tenant ─────────────────────────────────────────
TENANT_COLUMN=tenant_id
